<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language> en-US</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2023</copyright><pubDate> Tue, 01 Aug 2023 21:45:13 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[Zen moving game 'Unpacking' comes to Android and iOS on August 24th]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>如果您的放松想法涉及打开纸板箱，那么您将会度过一段愉快的时光。 Humble Games 和 Witch Beam 已 <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/PlayHumbleGames/status/1686440615356092434">确认</a><a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/unpacking-heads-to-phones-and-tablets-later-this-year-192946616.html"><em>《Unpacking》</em></a>将于 8 月 24 日登陆 iOS 和 Android。今天您可以以 10 美元的价格<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2FwcHMuYXBwbGUuY29tL3VzL2FwcC91bnBhY2tpbmcvaWQ2NDUwMDU4MTM1IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4ZjY2YTIwOS03ZjllLTQyZmEtOTYyYS03NjhhMWQ1ZDBmMzYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAZgVKbp_8xmMlxkhNdWlfaEozxJSt_XhA57bsRfHT1H1&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Funpacking%2Fid6450058135" class="rapid-with-clickid">预订</a>iOS 版本。鉴于该游戏于 2021 年首次登陆游戏机和 PC，这已经是一个漫长的时间了，但如果您是这个概念的新手，那么这可能是值得的。</p><p>从本质上讲， <em>《拆包》</em>是一款混合益智游戏和家居装饰游戏。当一个看不见的人搬进新住所时，你必须找到放置物品的空间。没有时间限制或其他压力，当您布置孩子的卧室或家庭厨房时，它可以非常舒缓。然而，它讲述故事的方式特别聪明。你是通过观察一个女人去了哪里以及她带来了什么来了解她的生活，而不是通过对话。由于标题几乎完全无字，因此很多人都可以理解。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="c2d36e6820c34dabb916361e923a6b1c"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TkRO7muHNQQ?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p>随着转向移动设备，游戏并没有发生显着变化。然而，开发人员认为<em>Unpacking</em>对于触摸来说是“完美的”，因为你可以用手指拖动对象并通过触觉反馈感知世界。不管这是否属实，便携性可能很有吸引力。当您刚搬到一个新地方时，这可能是最适合玩的游戏 - 您可以在常用的游戏硬件还没有收拾好时就启动它。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/zen-moving-game-unpacking-comes-to-android-and-ios-on-august-24th-214513079.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/zen-moving-game-unpacking-comes-to-android-and-ios-on-august-24th-214513079.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 8f66a209-7f9e-42fa-962a-768a1d5d0f36</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 21:45:13 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690924640</ingested><modified> 2023-08-01T21:17:23+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Small Businesses]]></category><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/a747b760-30ab-11ee-b23f-e439d370288a" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:conten